<lb n="0791a19" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0791a20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0791a21" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 517</head>
<lb n="0791a22" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說末羅王經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0791a23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0791a24" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">宋居士沮渠京聲譯</byline>
<lb n="0791a25" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0791a2501">聞如是：</p><p id="pT14p0791a2504" place="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，與
<lb n="0791a26" ed="T"/>千二百五十比丘俱。</p><p id="pT14p0791a2609" place="inline">時有國王，號曰末羅，土
<lb n="0791a27" ed="T"/>地豐沃，士民壯勇。其國中有方石，周旋數
<lb n="0791a28" ed="T"/>十里，當於王道。群臣共議，啟王徙石。王便
<lb n="0791a29" ed="T"/>料選國內，凡得九億人，令掘徙石，乃歷年
<pb n="0791b" ed="T" id="T14.0517.0791b"/>
<lb n="0791b01" ed="T"/>月，<note n="0791001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">士＝人【明】</note><app n="0791001"><lem wit="【大】">士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人</rdg></app>民疲極，不能動石。</p><p id="pT14p0791b0110" place="inline">佛念人民愚癡，空
<lb n="0791b02" ed="T"/>自勤苦，而石不移，即呼阿難：「<note n="0791002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔與〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔與〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791002"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>汝俱往。」如
<lb n="0791b03" ed="T"/>彈指頃，便到其國。</p><p id="pT14p0791b0308" place="inline">佛時作沙門，被服住<note n="0791003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791003"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於</rdg></app>
<lb n="0791b04" ed="T"/>石邊，謂人民言：「用何故掘徙此石？」初無應
<lb n="0791b05" ed="T"/>者，如是至三，人民恚言：「我掘此石，勤苦<note n="0791004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輕＝經【宮】</note><note n="0791004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輕＝經【宮】【麗-CB】【CB】</note><app n="0791004"><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" cf1="KI20n0848_p1193a14" wit="【CBETA】【麗】" cf2="T14n0517_p0791a29">經</lem><rdg wit="【大】">輕</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">經</rdg></app>
<lb n="0791b06" ed="T"/>年，卿何等人，反來問我？」各自委去。</p><p id="pT14p0791b0614" place="inline">佛即時
<lb n="0791b07" ed="T"/>笑，以足指挑石，手受之，<note n="0791005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擲＝挑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擲＝挑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791005"><lem wit="【大】">擲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">挑</rdg></app>置空中，復以手
<lb n="0791b08" ed="T"/>受，住之於地。佛便放光明、現相好，九億人見
<lb n="0791b09" ed="T"/>佛威神，莫不震<note n="0791006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聳＝悚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聳＝悚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791006"><lem wit="【大】">聳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悚</rdg></app>，皆叩頭言：「吾等愚癡，不
<lb n="0791b10" ed="T"/>別真偽，將何神天？」</p><p id="pT14p0791b1008" place="inline">佛言：「我是佛也。」</p><p id="pT14p0791b1014" place="inline">人民問
<lb n="0791b11" ed="T"/>言：「佛用何等力能舉此石？」答言：「我<note n="0791007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝以【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有＝以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791007"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以</rdg></app>四<note n="0791008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＋（舉此石）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力＋（舉此石）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791008"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">力舉此石</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0791b12" ed="T"/>何等為四？一為精進力、二為忍辱力、三為
<lb n="0791b13" ed="T"/>布施力、四為父母力。</p><p id="pT14p0791b1309" place="inline">「何等為精進力？謂不
<lb n="0791b14" ed="T"/>殺盜婬欺，廣陳經法，開導人物，未曾懈怠，
<lb n="0791b15" ed="T"/>是為精進力。</p><p id="pT14p0791b1506" place="inline">「何等為忍辱力？敢有殘害毀辱，
<lb n="0791b16" ed="T"/>加惡於我，我心如地，無所不受，是為忍辱
<lb n="0791b17" ed="T"/>力。</p><p id="pT14p0791b1702" place="inline">「何等為布施力？謂以國土珍寶妻子頭眼，
<lb n="0791b18" ed="T"/>悉以施人，意無恨悔，是為布施力。</p><p id="pT14p0791b1814" place="inline">「何等為
<lb n="0791b19" ed="T"/>父母力？謂受父母身體哺乳育養之恩，或從
<lb n="0791b20" ed="T"/>地積珍寶，上至二十八天，悉以施人，不如
<lb n="0791b21" ed="T"/>供養父母，是為父母力。」</p><p id="pT14p0791b2110" place="inline">人民復問言：「盡復
<lb n="0791b22" ed="T"/>有何等力？」</p><p id="pT14p0791b2205" place="inline">佛言：「復有四力。何等為四？謂生、
<lb n="0791b23" ed="T"/>老、病、死是為四力。」</p><p id="pT14p0791b2308" place="inline">復問言：「佛當常住於世
<lb n="0791b24" ed="T"/>不？」</p><p id="pT14p0791b2402" place="inline">佛言：「我亦當般泥洹。」</p><p id="pT14p0791b2410" place="inline">人民言：「佛乃神聖，
<lb n="0791b25" ed="T"/>相好金色，當世希有，猶尚般泥洹，何況我
<lb n="0791b26" ed="T"/>曹？」王及臣民，九億人同時意解，乞受五戒十
<lb n="0791b27" ed="T"/>善，歸命三尊，結解垢除，即得須陀洹道。</p><p id="pT14p0791b2716" place="inline">阿
<lb n="0791b28" ed="T"/>難<note n="0791009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝整【明】</note><app n="0791009"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">整</rdg></app>衣服，為佛作禮白言：「是王及與九億
<lb n="0791b29" ed="T"/>人，皆有何功德，今聞經即得解疾？」</p><p id="pT14p0791b2914" place="inline">佛言：「乃
<pb n="0791c" ed="T" id="T14.0517.0791c"/>
<lb n="0791c01" ed="T"/>昔俱留<note n="0791010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">秦＝先【三】【宮】</note><note n="0791010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">秦＝先【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0791010"><lem wit="【大】">秦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">先</rdg></app>佛時，王及國中九億人，同時立
<lb n="0791c02" ed="T"/>志，或受五戒十善者、或持齋者、或然燈者、或
<lb n="0791c03" ed="T"/>燒香散華者、或諷誦經者<note n="0791011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或〕－【宮】</note><app n="0791011"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>聽經者，今故來
<lb n="0791c04" ed="T"/>會，聞經即解。」</p><p id="pT14p0791c0406" place="inline">諸比丘歡喜，前為佛作禮。</p></div1>
<lb n="0791c05" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說末羅王經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>